        <Parent_String>lumber by technique: sawing method [300012802], lumber by technique [300137630], lumber [300012785], wood by product [300012779], wood and wood by product [300011913], plant material [300124117], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
